title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jun 23 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jun 23 2022
description:
The Biden Stasi: Feds raid home of former Trump DOJ official in connection with Jan. 6. CNN: House Dems have no interest in Biden's gas tax holiday. Biden's carrying out Green New Deal policies, wants higher gas prices, but can't tell the truth about it. Karine Jean-Pierre: "No working theory" on domestic energy production. Granholm: Higher gas prices are necessary to end reliance on fossil fuels. Buck takes a call from firefighter on the Uvalde response.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
